fields.value: Extracted Data From: ENERGY STAR Certified Product Data Sets and APIs

dsDescriptionValue.value:
This submission includes publicly available data extracted in its original form. Please reference the Related Publication listed here for source and citation information


In addition to the consumer product finders for ENERGY STAR certified models, EPA maintains 50+ related product data sets that are updated daily. The interface for these data sets allow users to generate a variety of reports, to create accounts for saving and sharing their work and to export data in a variety of different formats. EPA offers a guide on how to analyze these data sets and create data visualizations. [Quote from https://www.energystar.gov/productfinder/advanced] >

If you have questions or recommendations related to this metadata entry and extracted data, please contact the CAFE Data Management team at: climatecafe@bu.edu.
